/#
 A type used to report the status of a position.
 #/
enum FpML5.reporting.PositionStatusEnum {
    # The position is open and has been newly added since the last position report.
    New 
    # The position is open and was present in the last position report.
    Existing 
    # The position is no longer open, for example because it has matured, was assigned, or was terminated.
    Closed 

}

New.Doc: The position is open and has been newly added since the last position report.
New.Name: New

Existing.Doc: The position is open and was present in the last position report.
Existing.Name: Existing

Closed.Doc: The position is no longer open, for example because it has matured, was assigned, or was terminated.
Closed.Name: Closed
